{"tid":1916601,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"當年黑死病改變左世界政治經濟","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T08:33:07.000Z","uid":30791,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aad43542b95e10daa4dbd4826aa2a48cc955a7b1","tid":1916601,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"黑死病對歐洲人口造成嚴重影響，改變歐洲的社會結構，動搖當時支配歐洲的羅馬天主教會的地位，並因此使得一些少數族群受到迫害，例如猶太人、穆斯林、外國人、乞丐以及痲瘋病患者。生存與否的不確定性，使得人們產生「活在當下」的一種情緒，如同薄伽丘在《十日談》（The Decameron）之中所描繪的一般。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/黑死病\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%BB%91%E6%AD%BB%E7%97%85&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=8f7404ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/黑死病</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black_Death\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBlack_Death&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=4c4f8546\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black_Death</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black_Death#Consequences\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBlack_Death%23Consequences&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=b36b4f4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black_Death#Consequences</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Consequences_of_the_Black_Death\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FConsequences_of_the_Black_Death&d=rROtLXfiIyO0AijGL7caM0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=8a2ae14b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Consequences_of_the_Black_Death</a>"},{"pid":"78b29f39f3d7d24f0877313503faca08604f7a69","tid":1916601,"uid":17397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}